task.summary: Default task
UI Update
Air Tower Rework, removed cruft from save file, save tower fix.
Added farm mode, updated tooltips.
Replaced Vex with jQuery UI.
Hopefully fixed the frozen bug once and for all.
Forgot to add jQuery UI files.
Added load/save, credits screen, and some jquery UI files that were missed last time.
Added gulp file which concatenates javascript and css files. Reduces the sprite image size, changed sprite image to use JSON instead of XML.
Added the build directory, dirty but necessary for github.io.
Added the build directory, dirty but necessary for github.io.
Hopefully fixed css issue by removing css minification.
CSS Fix Pt 4: It turns out minification causes fewer issues than not including the proper sources in your gulp file.
Would also help to add the main sprite file to versioning.
Overhauled elemental system (yet again), added several new skills, several small bug fixes.
Added mana bar, teleport tweaks, elemental tower tweaks.
Experimental switch from accordions to jQuery UI menu.
Reduced extraneous whitespace.
Added a full data table for skills.
Added skill queuing and reworked skills UI.
Added skill queuing and reworked skills UI.
Added spells, refactored cursor logic, and made path recovery on recalculation better.
Fixed some cursor issues and added the ability to cancel.
Added frost spell.
Lots of skill improvements, added a couple of skills and the bleeding status effect.
Added prestige system and several skills.
Reworked prestige to only impact learn rate and added a clear queue button.
Added remove-from-queue button, several updates related to boss powers, various code cleanup.
Added skills markdown document to hopefully replace the old word document.
Updates to the skills markdown document.
Added keybinding, overhauled menu, additional checks on cursor overlays.
Added keybinding, overhauled menu, additional checks on cursor overlays.
Corrected tooltips for elemental towers.
Overhauled magic system, reworked mana regeneration, many quality of life improvements.
Added prev. wave and a preview of skill times.
Fixed prestige reset not reseting spell level.
Fixed load bug where towers weren't being cleaned up pre-load.
Implemented sensors skill, keybinding quality of life changes, added mana regeneration (advanced) skill.
Updated TODO and readme.
Added new help system, nerfed upgrade bonuses on towers outside of damage,

Merge branch 'gh-pages' of https://github.com/mbellifa/inctower into gh-pages
# Conflicts: # README.md
Visual indicators for tower power, tower range and fire rate nerf is now enforced even from old saves.
Reworked tower templates, added ability for cursor updates to all actions, added a new category of user action.
Added blueprint/template icon.
Fixed critical bugs with prestige not reseting tower blueprints and block gold generation.

* Mana Burst has been changed to only have the possiblity of mana pool increase at 33% or lower mana but now causes extra damage when above 90% mana. * You can no longer sell or scrap towers if you're down to your last tower. * Escape now allows you to deselect units. * No longer instructs the player to press shift erroneously. * Template scrapping is no longer allowed after prestige without the appropriate skill. * When loading saves towers will now respect the save unless the save would cause the tower to have greater range or fire rate than a new tower would be able to have.
Hopefully fixed the upgrade all lag issue.
Fixed subtle timing issue that may have caused several bugs including towers firing at the same time despite different fire rates.
Upgraded phaser to 2.4.7, timing issues part 2, added support for performance.now().
Updated many libraries, hopefully fixed the IE11 memory leak.
